	(text "ILIM = V_MEASURE = V_ADD / 2 - ((IA + IB + IC)) * GAIN / 3\nILIM_RECIR will dictate whether this brakes or coasts\nBraking can cause high current\n\nV_ADD = 3.3 V\nGAIN = {0.15,0.3,0.6,1.2} V/A\nIA + IB + IC = 2 A\nV_MEAUSURE = 1.25\n\nGAIN can control the current limit of the motors\n\nILI\nV_MEASURE = 1.75"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 22.86 182.88 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left top)
		)
		(uuid "792e1408-ba5a-4cba-b57e-81fa342f4a65")
	)
	(text "nFault is Open Drain so can be chained together\nActually could cause the others to go into a test mode so avoid possibly"
